    "%@%@, difficulty %lld" : {
      "comment" : "A text label describing a song, including its title, artist (if available), and difficulty level. The text is presented in a vertical stack with a headline font for the title and a subheadline font for the artist (if available). A spacer is included between the title and the artist, and a label indicating the difficulty level is appended to the end.",
